headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 4/20 Only Gifts and Bonuses
content:
This Tuesday, visit Ammu-Nation to collect the High Flyer Parachute Bag. Then head over to Binco or Ponsonby’s to pick up the gratis Green Space Horror Suit and get some free Green Tire Smoke from LS Customs.

You’ll also receive the Black Rockstar Camo & White Rockstar Camo Shirts just for playing.

And turn an profit by visiting Cayo Perico — you’ll be paid double for all the Weed you can stuff into your Loot Bag.

The gifts and bonuses listed above are all available exclusively on April 20.
